<li><i>Die Söhne</i> (<i>The Jews of Rome</i>), 1935</li>
<li><i>Der Tag wird kommen</i> (<i>The day will come</i>, <i>Josephus and the Emperor</i>), 1942</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><i>Flavius Josephus Eyewitness to Rome's first-century conquest of Judea</i>, Mireille Hadas-lebel, Macmillan 1993, Simon and Schuster 2001</li>
<li><i>The 2000 Year Old Middle East Policy Expert</i>, Give War A Chance, <a href="/wiki/P_J_O%27Rourke" title="P J O'Rourke" class="mw-redirect">P J O'Rourke</a><sup id="cite_ref-11" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-11" title=""><span>[</span>12<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
